<p>This Apollo 11 flight suit worn by Neil Armstrong (AAE’55, HDR E’70) is part of the Neil A. Armstrong papers, donated to the Purdue Archives over a number of years by Armstrong and his wife, Carol. The blue cloth training suit was common to Apollo and shuttle-era astronauts.</p>
