<h3 class="p150-item-detail__title" id="4925-lightbox-title">BGR Beacon</h3>
<div class="p150-item-detail__description">
<p> Each August, Purdue welcomes incoming freshmen for Boiler Gold Rush. With a record-setting 8,357 freshmen in 2018, student leaders have their work cut out for them making sure that new students don’t get lost. BGR leaders craft personalized beacons reflecting everything from pop culture to campus landmarks to carry throughout the week to help participants stay with their group. </p>
