<div class="p150-item-detail__description">
<p> The Cary Knight Spot Grill, located in the lower level of Cary Southeast, features a collection of a dozen or so wood tables immortalizing the graduating classes of Cary Quad men. Dozens more are in storage. The tables are rotated out periodically. Each tabletop includes etchings and art from that year’s senior class, an honor reserved for students who spent all of their undergraduate years living at Cary Quadrangle.</p>
