<p> Affectionately dubbed ice polishers by students, utility vehicles equipped with snow brooms are a common sight in winter months. Crews take to the sidewalks between midnight and 4:00 a.m. to begin clearing snow before students trudge to 7:30 a.m. classes across campus. </p>
