<h3 class="p150-item-detail__title" id="2483-lightbox-title">Tech Phone</h3>
<div class="p150-item-detail__description">
<p> Elliott Hall of Music seats 6,005 people. It’s one of the largest proscenium theaters in the country. The ceiling soars 57 feet above the auditorium, and it’s a climb up 100 steps to get there from the stage floor. Theater technicians adjusting lighting instruments in the ceiling used this phone to call down and communicate with the technical director, office, and other Hall of Music staff. </p>
